WaitingCell - Class in cells
Class which defines the WaitingCell of the Game, when a player reaches a WaitingCell, he has to wait for a define number of rounds, or he can leave the cell if another player replaces him.
WaitingCell(int, int, int) - Constructor for class cells.WaitingCell
Constructor of a WaitingCell that creates a WaitingCell at the index given in parameters and set a waiting counter and a waiting time.
